data.description: Back on market - 02/28/24.  Multiple offers were received the first time we were on the market but the accepted offer was not ratified.   Your buyers get a second chance!  This beautiful large home is move in ready.  Larger model in this sub-division.  Freshly painted throughout.  Hardwood floors re-finished.  Lovely kitchen with remodeling and has eat-in area.  Open floor plan on main level and has a dining room and living room area.  Three bedrooms on upper level.  Primary suite with own master bath.  Fully finished walk out basement with rec room and den/4rth bedroom and storage area.  Prime location that is close to commuter routes, shopping and highly desirable schools.
